        </a>معايير الاختيار
      </h2><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 my-5"><li class="text-text-secondary mb-2 leading-relaxed">الاعتماد من زاتكا</li><li class="text-text-secondary mb-2 leading-relaxed">سهولة التكامل</li><li class="text-text-secondary mb-2 leading-relaxed">العربية الكاملة</li><li class="text-text-secondary mb-2 leading-relaxed">دعم فني عربي</li></ul><h2 id="ما-يجب-أن-يغطيه" class="group flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-14 mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-white/10">
        <a class="text-accent-green hover:text-white underline underline-offset-2" href="#ما-يجب-أن-يغطيه" class="opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity text-accent-green flex-shrink-0">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><p class="text-text-secondary leading-8 mb-6 text-[17px]"ath strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1" /></svg>
        </a>ما يجب أن يُغطيه
